---
title: Thai Basil Chicken Stir-Fry with Lime, Green Beans & Jasmine Rice
description: We love the saucy texture and addictively savory, peppery flavor of Thai basil chicken. Fortunately, this version is super speedy to whip up in your own kitchen. In just 20 minutes, you can have steamy jasmine rice, saucy chicken, tender green beans, and a sprinkle of spicy chili flakes if you want to amp up the heat. It’s safe to say it doesn’t get much better than this, folks.
